title: Dakine Slim Footstrap
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Slim Footstrap.
Slim Footstrap Features:
- Lightweight construction
- Minimal water absorption
- Molded dual density foam prevents collapsing
- 10mm or 15mm size increment adjustment hole options
- Single or double insert
